  "response": "The essay topics for the Civil Services Main Examination can vary by year. In 2002, candidates were asked to choose from the following essay topics:\n\n1. \"The role of the United Nations in promoting world peace.\"\n2. \"The impact of technology on human life.\"\n3. \"Women\u2019s empowerment and its impact on society.\"\n4. \"The importance of education in modern society.\"\n\nCandidates were required to write a comprehensive essay on one of these topics, demonstrating their analytical abilities, understanding of the subject matter, and writing skills. If you need more details or a specific analysis of any topic, feel free to ask!",
